videos.description: Megan Walker sets a nice screen and gets open for Christyn Williams' pass, finishing with a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Williams, Walker link up for pick-and-roll bucket) 2020/02/07

videos.headline: Williams, Walker link up for pick-and-roll bucket

videos.description: Anna Makurat makes a nice pass on the ground to Aubrey Griffin, who puts in a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Makurat's nice pass sets up Griffin for layup) 2020/02/07

videos.headline: Makurat's nice pass sets up Griffin for layup

videos.description: Memphis' Gazmyne Herndon lines up for the basket, but Aubrey Griffin jumps up and knocks it away.
videos.headline: Griffin rejects Herndon's layup

videos.description: Molly Bent turns defense into offense with a steal that she converts into a wide-open layup at the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Bent's steal leads to bucket) 2020/02/07

videos.headline: Bent's steal leads to bucket
